{"word":"H3225 - יָמִין - yâmîyn - yaw-meen' - Left-handed","slug":"H3225","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָמִין</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâmîyn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-meen'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Left-handed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05DE;&#x05D9;&#x05DF; - ya&#x0302;m&#x0131;&#x0302;yn</b> - <i>yaw-meen'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3231\">H3231</a>; the <i>right</i> hand or side (leg, eye) of a person or other object (as the <i>stronger</i> and more dexterous); locally, the <i>south: - </i> + left-handed, right (hand, side), south."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3226\">H3226</a>, <a href=\"#/H3227\">H3227</a>, <a href=\"#/H3228\">H3228</a>, <a href=\"#/H3231\">H3231</a>, <a href=\"#/H3232\">H3232</a>, <a href=\"#/H3233\">H3233</a>, <a href=\"#/H541\">H541</a>, <a href=\"#/H8486\">H8486</a>, <a href=\"#/H8487\">H8487</a>, <a href=\"#/H8488\">H8488</a>, <a href=\"#/H8489\">H8489</a>"}]}